Package org.neo4j.values.storable

Interface ValueWriter<E extends Exception>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - type of Exception thrown from writer methods.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AnyValueWriter<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppendOnlyValuesContainer.Writer, ArrayEncoder.ValueEncoder, BaseToObjectValueWriter, CompositeGenericKey, GenericKey, MessageMetadataParser.TransactionMetadataWriter, NativeIndexKey, Neo4jPackV1.PackerV1, Neo4jPackV2.PackerV2, PrettyPrinter, PrimitiveOnlyValueWriter, PropertyStore.PropertyBlockValueWriter, QueryStatusResult.ParameterWriter, ReferenceEntityValueWriter, TemporalValueWriterAdapter, ValueWriter.Adapter
    public interface ValueWriter<E extends Exception>
    Writer of values.

    Has functionality to write all supported primitives, as well as arrays and different representations of Strings.
